{"tid":492982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者台語街訪 年青人：聽不太懂 自我介紹都不會","createTime":"2017-12-08T05:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T14:04:55.000Z","uid":144372,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"8c49ddc5ed6c4d280272a4a4216ec724b71d7b7f","tid":492982,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DVsb8ySn7d4?t=53\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDVsb8ySn7d4%3Ft%3D53&d=jDd7n1Vz9sOp%2FOQjG5TxkU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c236d33f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DVsb8ySn7d4?t=53</a><br />\n<br />\n【民視即時新聞】台灣小學推行母語教育已經16年，但會講台語的年輕人還是似乎沒變多，有相關學者提出，20~30歲之間會聽說台語的年輕人不到50%，更大膽預言照這樣下去，台語恐怕會在30年內滅亡，對此文化部預計提出國家語言發展法草案，目前正召開公聽會，希望能救救台語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見琴日有post傾緊台仔D台語<br />\n比你哋睇吓篇新聞<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再有on9仔話咩台灣都好多人講<br />\n你睇吓識講D人幾多歲先<br />\n而家基本上藍綠都一致認為後生仔冇幾多個識台語"},{"pid":"f8e43dd29872096252d0ded1396249584ec56721","tid":492982,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":41,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"方言"},{"pid":"46dc440ba2a63e463bca295c8f604a762e185846","tid":492982,"uid":144372,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>方言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1949年全台不足10%人識國語<br />\n邊個係方言"},{"pid":"70c351d946097a10d523356d255520d02fbf69db","tid":492982,"uid":41818,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>方言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1949年全台不足10%人識國語<br />\n邊個係方言</blockquote><br />\n喺依家台灣人眼中係<br />\n可能當時D人忽視呢種失傳速度 所以廣東話要小心"},{"pid":"511c685ba037da169f3c80a7a819d7a731e88677","tid":492982,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5ebb4a8e0649de546beab21843880de3a27187c0","tid":492982,"uid":144372,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b